Class DataResource

java.lang.Object
dev.katsute.onemta.DataResource
public abstract class DataResource extends Object
Represents a static data resource. Latest data can be retrieved from http://web.mta.info/developers/developer-data-terms.html#data.

    • create

      public static DataResource create(DataResourceType type, File file)
      Creates a data resource from a zip file.
      At the moment the zip file only needs to have:
      • agency.txt
      • stops.txt
      • routes.txt
      All other files are ignored.
      Parameters:
      type - resource type
      file - google_transit zip file
      Returns:
      data resource
      Since:
      1.0.0
